# 4. Structural Diagrams & Schematics

## 4.1 Broadcast Receiver — End-to-End Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Source of Broadcast] --> B{Type of Sender}
    B -- System --> C[ActivityManagerService]
    B -- App --> C
    C --> D{Action Filter Match}
    D -- No Match --> Z[Receiver Ignored]
    D -- Match --> E[Resolve Target Receivers]
    E -- Static --> F[AndroidManifest.xml Receiver]
    E -- Dynamic --> G[Context-Registered Receiver]
    F --> H[onReceive Callback]
    G --> H
    H --> I{Heavy Work?}
    I -- No --> J[Return Immediately]
    I -- Yes --> K[goAsync / WorkManager Delegate]
    K --> L[Background Thread Execution]
