    M --> N[Next Broadcast Processed]
```

## 4.2 Content Provider — Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph ClientApp[Client Application]
        UI[Activity / UI] --> CR[ContentResolver Singleton]
    end

    subgraph ProviderApp[Provider Application]
        CP[ContentProvider Subclass]
        SQLite[(SQLite Database)]
        FS[(File System)]
        Net[(Network Source)]
    end

    CR -- "query() URI" --> CP
    CP -- "SQLiteQueryBuilder" --> SQLite
    CP -- "openFile()" --> FS
    CP -- "openConnection()" --> Net
