```

## 4.3 IoT App Integration — Combined Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Sensor as IoT Sensor / BLE Peripheral
    participant Service as Foreground Service
    participant Receiver as Broadcast Receiver
    participant Provider as Content Provider
    participant Observer as ContentObserver
    participant UI as Dashboard Activity

    Sensor->>Service: Disconnection Event
    Service->>Service: Build Intent with Extras
    Service->>Receiver: sendBroadcast(explicit)
    Receiver->>Receiver: onReceive() executes
    Receiver->>Provider: insert(sensor log)
    Provider->>Provider: SQLite write
    Provider-->>Observer: notifyChange(uri)
    Observer->>UI: onChange() callback
    UI->>UI: Update dashboard chart
    Receiver->>UI: Show notification
```

## 4.4 URI Matcher Decision Tree

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Incoming content URI] --> B{Authority Match?}
    B -- No --> X[Throw IllegalArgumentException]
    B -- Yes --> C{Path Pattern}
    C -- "sensor_readings" --> D[MATCH_READINGS - Dir]
    C -- "sensor_readings/42" --> E[MATCH_READING_ID - Item]
    C -- "devices/abc/config" --> F[Custom MATCH_SUBPATH]
    D --> G[query All Rows]
