> **(b) Design an Android application flow for a smart home IoT system where:**
> **(i) A `RoomListActivity` displays a list of rooms. When a user taps a room, the app passes the room name and an `ArrayList<Sensor>` of all sensors in that room to a `RoomControlActivity`. (4 marks)**
> **(ii) `RoomControlActivity` must return the updated "fan speed" (an integer 0-5) to `RoomListActivity` via the modern `ActivityResultLauncher` API. (3 marks)**
