# 4. Structural Diagrams & Schematics

## 4.1 Content Provider Architecture — End-to-End Block Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph AppA["CLIENT APPLICATION (App A)"]
        UI_A[Activity or Fragment]
        CR[Content Resolver]
    end

    subgraph AndroidSys["ANDROID SYSTEM SERVER"]
        Binder[Process Binder / IPC]
        PermChk[Permission Check]
    end

    subgraph AppB["PROVIDER APPLICATION (App B)"]
        CP[Content Provider Implementation]
        URI_M[Uri Matcher]
        DBHelper[SQLite Open Helper]
        SQL[SQLite Database]
    end

    UI_A -->|getContentResolver| CR
    CR -->|insert / query / update / delete| Binder
    Binder --> PermChk
    PermChk -->|Authorized| CP
    CP --> URI_M
    URI_M -->|Switch on code| DBHelper
    DBHelper --> SQL
    SQL -->|Rows| DBHelper
    DBHelper -->|Cursor or count| CP
    CP -->|Result| Binder
    Binder -->|Cursor or count| CR
    CR --> UI_A
```

## 4.2 CRUD Operation Flow — Sequential

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client App
    participant R as ContentResolver
    participant S as Android System
    participant P as ContentProvider
    participant D as SQLite Database

    Note over C,P: INSERT FLOW
    C->>R: insert(uri, ContentValues)
    R->>S: Binder IPC call
    S->>P: invoke insert(uri, cv)
    P->>D: db.insert(TABLE, null, cv)
    D-->>P: rowId
    P->>S: notifyChange(uri)
    P-->>R: newUri
    R-->>C: newUri

    Note over C,P: QUERY FLOW
    C->>R: query(uri, proj, sel, args, sort)
    R->>S: Binder IPC call
    S->>P: invoke query(...)
    P->>D: db.query(...)
    D-->>P: Cursor
    P-->>R: Cursor
    R-->>C: Cursor

    Note over C,P: UPDATE FLOW
    C->>R: update(uri, cv, sel, args)
    R->>S: Binder IPC call
    S->>P: invoke update(...)
    P->>D: db.update(...)
    D-->>P: rowsAffected
    P->>S: notifyChange(uri)
    P-->>R: count
    R-->>C: count

    Note over C,P: DELETE FLOW
    C->>R: delete(uri, sel, args)
    R->>S: Binder IPC call
    S->>P: invoke delete(...)
    P->>D: db.delete(...)
    D-->>P: rowsAffected
    P->>S: notifyChange(uri)
    P-->>R: count
    R-->>C: count
```

## 4.3 URI Resolution Decision Tree

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start[Incoming Content URI] --> Match{UriMatcher.match uri}
    Match -->|100| Table[Entire table<br/>code READINGS]
    Match -->|101| Row[Single row by ID<br/>code READING BY ID]
    Match -->|-1| Error[Throw IllegalArgumentException]

    Table --> Q1{Query}
    Table --> I1{Insert}
    Table --> U1{Update}
    Table --> D1{Delete}

    Row --> QR{Single row query}
    Row --> UR{Single row update}
    Row --> DR{Single row delete}
```
